{"tid":2043070,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國防七校 四間被美禁購零件","createTime":"2020-05-30T07:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T07:39:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db9c554856c725af52fef0afbcc7afc746d9b66f","tid":2043070,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200530/2AACXWCVZVIDNCHG6YC6LB4CXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200530%2F2AACXWCVZVIDNCHG6YC6LB4CXU%2F&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=4b3595c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200530%2F2AACXWCVZVIDNCHG6YC6LB4CXU%2F&h=bdd9062e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200530/2AACXWCVZVIDNCHG6YC6LB4CXU/</a><br />\n<br />\n國防七校 四間被美禁購零件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NCGUCC2OTOQMHEQQ5IFU3PNKZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNCGUCC2OTOQMHEQQ5IFU3PNKZY.jpg&h=b16b24a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北京航空航天大學為國防七校之一，是中國國防領域的中流砥柱。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n《紐時》報道中提及與中國軍方關係密切的國防七校（亦稱國防七子），是指中國工業信息化部下屬、包括北京航空航天大學的七間院校。每年培養超過一萬名畢業生進入國防研究領域，其中博士畢業生最受追捧，僱主包括生產軍用產品的國防集團、華為、中興等高科技公司。目前七校中，已經有四間院校被美國商務部列入實體清單，要接受「華為式待遇」，即在未獲美國政府批准的情況下，禁止從美國購入零件。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：專家：倘華不改善勢打金融戰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一大學經費較澳洲國防部多<br />\n<br />\n七間院校分別是北京航空航天大學、北京理工大學、哈爾濱工業大學、西北工業大學、哈爾濱工程大學、南京航空航天大學、南京理工大學，是中國國防領域的中流砥柱。例如殲20戰機。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n七校獲得政府的雄厚資金，約一半研究支出用於國防研究。2018年，其中四校的每名研究人員經費位列中國大學前五名，單單是哈爾濱工業。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n就在上周，美國商務部將哈爾濱工業大學、哈爾濱工程大學加入「實體清單」，禁止其在未得到美方批准之下。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲戰略政策學會"},{"pid":"0094f767f9205f39c5fd453e6d9b53565b914739","tid":2043070,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:30:52.000Z","msg":"比人貪曬好意思講一半研究支出用於國防研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af244199216c093e57d7f945991e7f4b06efe09","tid":2043070,"uid":73569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0094f767f9205f39c5fd453e6d9b53565b914739","tid":2043070,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:30:52.000Z","msg":"比人貪曬好意思講一半研究支出用於國防研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:39:52.000Z","msg":"美軍扮弱就係想囉多d軍費做研究同裝備<br />\n支那扮強就係想囉多d軍費去貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}